  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Developing a campaigns supporter base in Wales</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will recruit new activists by attending and organising events and targeted leafleting through Oxfam shops and other outlets. We will retain and build the capacity of existing members by providing bilingual campaign resources, organising networking events and training. We will raise the profile of the groups through our own channels (online, media support etc.) plus give support for groups to generate their own publicity. We shall also coordinate and network groups as part of &#x2018;One Oxfam&apos; so they support, and gain from connections with, trading and community fundraising activities in Wales.</narrative>
  </description>
